* {{ill|Inari Shrine|ja|稲荷神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Inari Shrine|qq=}}

== Access ==
* From JR {{ill|Azumigawa Station|ja|安曇川駅|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Azumigawa Station|qq=}}, take the {{ill|Kōjaku Bus|ja|江若バス|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōjaku Bus|qq=}} bound for Kuchiki Gakkō, get off at Nakano Bus Stop, and walk 8 minutes.

